Which would give decryption by miners a competitive advantage over out-of-system decryption
My idea was to find some algo where miners can work on decrypting all desired secrets in parallel
It's obviously only going to be secret up to some economic margin
The important part is the PoW coupling, so you can actually get secrets controlled by code (up to a cost margin)
Useful PoW idea: PoW that simultaneously decrypts secrets only if on-chain scripts say the secrets should be decrypted
